<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/26101749">如何在完全不会使用CFD软件的情况下装作很了解CFD的样子？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2623599" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
